## Getting Started

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m examples.demo
```

See [the examples directory](examples) for examples of using PyUI. Here's a [TodoMVC](http://todomvc.com) app:

![PyUI TodoMVC](docs/images/pyui-todomvc.png)
